HEADWORD: Dangler
<hw>Dan"gler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who dangles about
or after others, especially after women; a trifler.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧
<xex>Danglers</xex> at toilets.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
